  "prompt": "Why didn't Jennifer Hudson speak at the Republican Convention in support of Donald Trump?",
  "response": "Jennifer Hudson did not speak at the Republican Convention in support of Donald Trump due to a combination of personal beliefs and political affiliations. Hudson, a well-known singer, actress, and Democrat, has generally aligned with Democratic values and political figures. Her support has typically been directed toward Democratic candidates and causes, which are in contrast with the Republican Party and Donald Trump's policies. Consequently, it is unlikely for her to support or speak at an event promoting a politician whose views and actions she does not endorse.",
